data.title: Do vendors call out their products in the street?
data.meta_description: Answer: As we all know, in many cases, vendors do call out their products while selling on the street. This practice is often referred to as "street vending" or "hawkers" and is commonly seen in various parts of the world. Street vendors use vocal announcements to grab the attention of passersby ...
